MUT · S234 · Patricia Inversion Node · S234 · S234: MUT — THE INVERSE OF INFORMED-COMMAND

universe of origin : The temple of Karnak at Thebes — the great mother whose name simply means "mother," consort of Amun, queen of the gods, the vulture-crowned matriarch whose authority is birthright and not briefing, who commands as the womb commands, before any report is given
seal               : The informed command is holy precisely because the great mother proves a will can rule by origin alone, before any report arrives.
spoken token       : brax-sand-sei
